article.story: SAN ANTONIO -- — Chris Mullins registered 15 points as Rice defeated Incarnate Word 68-53 in a on Friday. Travis Evee had 12 points for Rice (1-0). Max Fiedler added 12 points. Keaston Willis had 22 points for the Cardinals (0-1). Drew Lutz added 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
